com.foreach.imageserver.dto

Class CropDto

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.foreach.imageserver.dto.CropDto

  • public class CropDto
extends Object
    Source dimensions are the assumed dimensions of the original image. Basically they define the scale of the coordinate system. If not set, the original dimensions of the target image are assumed unless a box is defined. In the latter case the box will be used to scale down the original and then use those coordinates as source.
